\\\\ While loops in Sigi
\\\\ [ body ] loops while stack top is nonzero
\\\\ Stack top is the counter; body should update it for next iteration

\\\\ Count down from 5:
\\\\ Pattern: push counter, while loop
\\\\ Body: @ dup, | print, !1 - decrement
\\\\ At end of body, stack top is new counter

!5 [ @ | !1 - ]
$                      \\\\ leave clean (drops final 0)

